The cave is easy to find with the help of the beacon. It is well
camoflaged, but the beacon takes TUSCON right to it.

TORCA stepped to the entrance of the cave, his thick frame covered in
battle scars and wounds, but he seemed to be fairly okay. AIRHAMMER is
standing over the heavily wounded forms of BANTOR and SILVERBOLT as
they lay down in the back of the cave.

&quot;We just got our radios working again.&quot; TORCA said without much
preamble. &quot;We were about to call for an evac when we got NOCTORRO&#39;s
call. I think most of us are okay, although Bantor will need some time
in the CR chamber.&quot;

TORCA pointed at SILVERBOLT, &quot;But he got it the worst of it. The
seekers hit him with some sort of extraction device right on his spark
chamber. Bantor dove in and knocked it away, but the backlash damaged
them both.&quot;

AIRHAMMER nodded, &quot;After that we drove them off, but Bantor and
Silverbolt were damaged.&quot; AIRHAMMER looked down at them. &quot;We don&#39;t
know how the damage is to Silverbolt. He has not awakened yet.&quot;

